OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FLilac house in Watford     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fconservation area may have 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fto be repainted            
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A man living in a conservation area who
OL,6, painted his house lilac may have to    
OL,7, redecorate it.                         
OL,9,FIan Davis, who lives in Oxhey in       
OL,10,FHertfordshire, painted his property in 
OL,11,FAugust 2020 and was told in June he    
OL,12,Fshould have sought planning permission.
OL,14,FHis retrospective application was      
OL,15,Frejected by Watford Borough Council    
OL,16,Fwhich said it had a "harmful impact" on
OL,17,Fthe character of the 1902-built home.  
OL,19,FIt said the colour was "inappropriate" 
OL,20,Ffor the period when it was built.      
